Resource Profile: HL7® AT Core Patient Profile

Official URL: http://fhir.hl7.at/elga-e-medikation-R5/StructureDefinition/at-core-patient Version: 0.0.0
Draft as of 2024-03-19 Responsible: ELGA GmbH Computable Name: HL7ATCorePatient

HL7® Austria FHIR® Core Profile for patient data in Austria. The HL7® AT Core Patient is based upon the core FHIR® Patient Resource and designed to meet the applicable patient demographic data elements in Austria. It identifies which core elements, extensions, vocabularies and value sets SHALL be present in the resource when using this profile. Note, this extension represents the common structure of Patient information within Austrian information systems.

Usage:

  • Refer to this Resource Profile: LINCA Dispense (LINCAMedicationDispense), LINCA Prescription (LINCAPrescriptionMedicationRequest) and LINCA Proposal Item (LINCAProposalMedicationRequest)
  • Examples for this Resource Profile: Patient/6800bda462034a9a8123e3dc48c61d53, Patient/d14e6251b3c545828f7e44cdc6faf2fb and Patient/ee8d340312484aaca84774b2a0d53533
